metadata.name: Fragile World
metadata.description:
The first art from series of arts call "The War is not a toy" by Luba Diker.
"Everyone who looks at these pictures feels a dangerous moment, a little more and a catastrophe will happen. This is what every person in our countries is feeling right now. I would like to show by my works that the Russian people are also against the war, we are horrified by what is happening now..."
